snippet.title: Official Call of Duty®: Black Ops III – Descent Multiplayer Trailer
snippet.description:
Descent, the third DLC map pack for Call of Duty®: Black Ops III, arrives first on PlayStation®4 on July 12. Prepare to battle through four new action-packed Multiplayer maps: Berserk, Cryogen, Rumble, and Empire, Treyarch’s bold reimagining of the Black Ops II classic map, Raid.

Pick up the Descent DLC Pack today: http://bit.ly/BO3Descent

Follow us for the latest intel:

Web: http://www.callofduty.com
Facebook: http://facebook.com/CallofDuty and http://facebook.com/Treyarch
Twitter: https://twitter.com/CallofDuty and https://twitter.com/Treyarch
